g4p.tool.controls

Class ListGen

  • java.lang.Object
    • g4p.tool.controls.ListGen
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TDataConstants

    public final class ListGen
extends Object
implements TDataConstants
    Singleton class used to create and store option lists for combobox editors.
    When adding a new type of list - need to modify the getValidator(type) method to included it.
    Author:
    Peter Lager.
